<p class="small-margin-before">Brand new “BCH PLS” T-shirt from the legendary bitcoin investor, early adopter of Bitcoin Roger Ver with his personal signature on the front. Roger Ver is one of the most known Bitcoin angel investors and evangelists. Learning about Bitcoin in 2011, he started investing in it at a price of about $1. Ver has made seed investments in many early Bitcoin startups, such as Blockchain.info and BitPay.com, which are now some of the most successful companies in their respective niches. Roger Ver is also famous for constantly working to promote Bitcoin and educate people about it. He frequently speaks at different conferences and meetups dedicated to Bitcoin and cryptocurrencies.</p> 
